metadata.description: Winner receives physical. https://www.emmaboudin.com/ Emma Boudin is a 21 year old graphic designer based in New York and Los Angeles. In her work she tends to explore the intersection between music and design. Her building client list includes artists such as Dance Yourself Clean, Loud Hound, Pink Skies and Burko. She believes that her design work is the collective that molds herself as a designer hence titling her practice, Boudin Collective.
